      <b data-is-speakable>In Anthony Bourdain Cookbook, 'Appetites,' He Pleases The Toughest Food Critic (His 9-Year-Old) : The Salt</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Anthony Bourdain's new cookbook features comfort food he cooks for his young daughter. "She's who I need to please, and if she's not happy, I'm not happy," he says.</b>
